  <article class="about__service service__multi" id="service-virtual-styling">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service letter-spacing">
        Virtual Styling
      </h4>
    </header>

    <p class="service__overview">
      I can assist you, near or far! The beauty of technology is that it can connect us from anywhere across the world. The desire to feel confident and assured is universal, so why limit ourselves to local influence?
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service service__virtual-consultation">
      <span class="title__sub-service"><em>New Client Consultation:​</em></span> A one hour FaceTime call to get to know you and your lifestyle. We will “walk through” your closet together to assess needs, wants, and items that are ready to purge! This is really a time for me to get to know you so that I can thoughtfully and intentionally build your wardrobe. We will get clear on the process and outline a game plan including budget and schedule.
    </p>

    <figure class="about__virtual" id="Alex-Sachel-Earing">
      <picture>
        {% set image_path %}/images/Service-Alex-Sachel-Virtual-Styling{% endset %}
        <img
          alt="An image of Alex Sachel, a Style Consultant based out of Chattanooga, TN."
          {% include "partials/ri-med-width.njk" %}
          >
      </picture>
    </figure>

    <p class="sub-service service__mood-board">
      <span class="title__sub-service"><em>Custom Mood Board:</em></span>​ I will send a customized mood/styling board that will include outfit examples, proportion updates, and styling advice. I love to work collaboratively to provide the best outcome, so I will explain my thought process while you provide specific feedback to ensure we are on the same page. I will make any necessary edits before we begin shopping; the fun part!
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service service__shopping-list">
      <span class="title__sub-service"><em>Shopping:</em></span> I will send you a personalized shop list of items for you to order at your own pace. Once items are ordered, we will jump on a FaceTime call to discuss fit along with styling and outfitting options to ensure that each item integrates seamlessly into your existing wardrobe.
    </p>

    <figure class="about__virtual" id="Alex-Sachel-Blue-Door">
      <picture>
        {% set image_path %}/images/Service-Alex-Sachel-Virtual-Styling-2{% endset %}
        <img
          alt="An image of Alex Sachel, a Style Consultant based out of Chattanooga, TN."
          {% include "partials/ri-med-width.njk" %}
